Snapshot 
⚙️ Basic Snapshot Operations
1. Create Snapshot
snapshot create -vserver vs1 -volume data_vol -snapshot snap1
2. View Snapshots
snapshot show
3. Delete Snapshot
snapshot delete -vserver vs1 -volume data_vol -snapshot snap1
4. Restore from Snapshot
snapshot restore -vserver vs1 -volume data_vol -snapshot snap1
🔁 Snapshot Policy (Automation)

👉 Automatically creates snapshots at intervals

snapshot policy create -policy daily_policy

👉 Attach to volume:

volume modify -vserver vs1 -volume data_vol -snapshot-policy daily_policy
